title: Barros Gomes (Henrique de)
body: He was in Funchal from July 8 to September 2, 1878, as the Director of the Bank of Portugal, due to the bankruptcy of João José Rodrigues Leitão, an agent of the same bank on this island. (See Banks).

João José Rodrigues Leitão: Agent of the Bank of Portugal

1878: Presence of Henrique de Barros Gomes in Funchal
